-- U.A.E. to Pass Bankruptcy Law Before Year-End, Alrroya Reports
-- B y   T a m a r a   W a l i d
-- 2012-05-15T10:19:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-15/u-a-e-to-pass-bankruptcy-law-before-year-end-alrroya-reports.html
The  United Arab Emirates  will pass a
bankruptcy law before the year end for listed and private
companies as well as family businesses,  Alrroya  reported today,
citing Minister of Justice Hadef Al Dhaheri.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tamara Walid in Abu Dhabi at 
 twalid@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Maher Chmaytelli at 
 mchmaytelli@bloomberg.net  